# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:39
translate spanish hwb_s17_0d05e07e:

    # "Even when the box is closed it radiates a heavy aura, one that’s weightiness is almost intimidating whenever I come near it."
    "Incluso cuando la caja está cerrada, irradia un aura pesada, cuyo peso es casi intimidante cada vez que me acerco."

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:44
translate spanish hwb_s17_6b66b607:

    # "I place it in the drawer and seal it away, a sigh of relief following."
    "La coloco en el cajón y la guardo, seguido de un suspiro de alivio."

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:48
translate spanish hwb_s17_74592b50:

    # Amber "Two down, one to go."
    Amber "Две части нашли, осталась одна."

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:53
translate spanish hwb_s17_eaec22ab:

    # Marina "Whoa, there’s only one more piece left?"
    Marina "Ничего себе, всего одна?"

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:57
translate spanish hwb_s17_a388fb42:

    # Amber "I think so. There's only some experts writing about \"historical relevance\" after the next entry."
    Amber "Думаю, да. Есть лишь несколько экспертных мнений о “исторической точности” после следующей записи."

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:61
translate spanish hwb_s17_81155f13:

    # "Flopping down on the couch next to Marina, I take a sip of my coffee and flip to the final entry of the journal."
    "Dejándome caer en el sofá junto a Marina, tomo un sorbo de mi café y paso a la última entrada del diario."

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:63
translate spanish hwb_s17_fd91c0c3:

    # "Marina glosses over the page, a hazy look forming in her eyes as she soaks it in."
    "Marina hojea la página, una mirada nebulosa formándose en sus ojos mientras la absorbe."

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:67
translate spanish hwb_s17_6c0271ef:

    # Marina "I can’t believe it’s almost over."
    Marina "Не могу поверить, что почти все кончено."

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:71
translate spanish hwb_s17_9b4c94a6:

    # Amber "Yeah, it’s weird that it hasn’t even been that long."
    Amber "Да, странно, что все это не заняло у нас особо много времени."

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:73
translate spanish hwb_s17_6aeebb2f:

    # "The motorhome goes quiet, the buzz of the generator humming in the background."
    "La casa rodante se queda en silencio, el zumbido del generador sonando de fondo."

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:77
translate spanish hwb_s17_3b22f551:

    # Amber "Well it’s not over yet! We still gotta figure out where it is, and then there’s still the search!"
    Amber "Но еще не все! Нам по-прежнему надо выяснить, где спрятана последняя часть, а потом еще и найти ее!"

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:79
translate spanish hwb_s17_7c3c90bc:

    # "I think Marina’s enthusiasm is becoming infectious."
    "Creo que el entusiasmo de Marina se está volviendo contagioso."

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:81
translate spanish hwb_s17_3245c338:

    # "She simply nods, now just gazing into her lap."
    "Ella simplemente asiente, ahora mirando fijamente su regazo."

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:83
translate spanish hwb_s17_d4355b35:

    # Amber "Well, let’s see what it says."
    Amber "Что ж, давай посмотрим, что там сказано."

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:95
translate spanish hwb_s17_31d56783:

    # "I was never certain about the other locations, and considering how many giant rocks, canyons, and arches are in this country, most of them were probably just a fluke."
    "Nunca estuve segura de las otras ubicaciones, y considerando cuántas rocas gigantes, cañones y arcos hay en este país, la mayoría probablemente fueron solo una casualidad."

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:97
translate spanish hwb_s17_dc82e86d:

    # "But this is unmistakable."
    "Pero esto es inconfundible."

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:99
translate spanish hwb_s17_8f0ccd8f:

    # "The vivid and breathtaking imagery, the constant allusions to flames, and most importantly—the heat."
    "Las imágenes vívidas y impresionantes, las constantes alusiones a llamas, y lo más importante: el calor."

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:103
translate spanish hwb_s17_170fe553:

    # Amber "He hid it in the Valley of Fire."
    Amber "Он спрятал его в Долине Огня."

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:107
translate spanish hwb_s17_8e30fe71:

    # "Marina snaps back to attention, my conviction pulling her back from Marina-Land."
    "Marina vuelve a prestar atención, mi convicción la saca de la Tierra de Marina."

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:109
translate spanish hwb_s17_8c643f6e:

    # Marina "Are you sure?"
    Marina "Ты уверена?"

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:111
translate spanish hwb_s17_cd7a4476:

    # Amber "Positive. There’s no other place it could be."
    Amber "Абсолютно. Другого варианта, где оно может быть, просто нет."

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:115
translate spanish hwb_s17_8f7a1145:

    # Marina "Oh."
    Marina "Ох."

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:121
translate spanish hwb_s17_6bda9bad:

    # "She might as well have shot down my momentum with an elephant gun."
    "Bien podría haber derribado mi impulso con un rifle de elefante."

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:127
translate spanish hwb_s17_574a279e:

    # Amber "‘Oh?’ That’s all?"
    Amber "“Ох”? И это все?"

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:131
translate spanish hwb_s17_de06bbdb:

    # Marina "Yep."
    Marina "Ага."

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:133
translate spanish hwb_s17_b860d29d:

    # Amber "No \"Oooh? What’s that, a place always on fire?\""
    Amber "Никаких “Ооох? Это место что, постоянно в огне?”"

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:137
translate spanish hwb_s17_086c9c39:

    # "She narrows her eyes to an unimpressed squint. If they could shoot lasers, they would be right now."
    "Entrecerra los ojos en un gesto poco impresionado. Si pudieran disparar láseres, lo harían ahora mismo."

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:141
translate spanish hwb_s17_ad150e13:

    # Marina "Amber, how dumb do you think I am?"
    Marina "Эмбер, насколько я тупая, по-твоему?"

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:145
translate spanish hwb_s17_ce0bc664:

    # Amber "I didn’t say you were du—"
    Amber "Я не говорила, что ты ту—"

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:149
translate spanish hwb_s17_4a255414:

    # Marina "Always on fire? Really?"
    Marina "Постоянно в огне? Серьезно?"

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:153
translate spanish hwb_s17_8b323072:

    # Amber "Now I feel dumb for saying it."
    Amber "Теперь я чувствую себя тупой за сказанное."

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:155
translate spanish hwb_s17_fa7d0cfa:

    # Marina "You probably should."
    Marina "Вероятно, так ты и должна себя чувствовать."

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:157
translate spanish hwb_s17_1263e952:

    # "Ouch."
    "Ay."

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:161
translate spanish hwb_s17_8710fa4d:

    # "If her enthusiasm is infectious then so is my unrelenting realism. It’s corrupting her innocence."
    "Si su entusiasmo es contagioso, entonces mi realismo implacable también lo es. Está corrompiendo su inocencia."

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:165
translate spanish hwb_s17_e16c2741:

    # Marina "By the way, what’s the Valley of Fire?"
    Marina "Кстати, что такое Долина Огня?"

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:167
translate spanish hwb_s17_54004d25:

    # "Well, maybe not too infectious."
    "Bueno, tal vez no tan infeccioso."

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:169
translate spanish hwb_s17_7483ad79:

    # "Massaging my scalp, I shake my hair, hopefully creating enough new wrinkles in my brain that will help with explaining this."
    "Masajeando mi cuero cabelludo, sacudo mi cabello, con la esperanza de crear suficientes arrugas nuevas en mi cerebro que ayuden a explicar esto."

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:173
translate spanish hwb_s17_1d1fc718:

    # Amber "Alright, so take a whole bunch of rocks, sand, and dirt. Okay?"
    Amber "Хорошо, представь кучу камней, песка и земли. Представила?"

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:177
translate spanish hwb_s17_69d7b147:

    # Marina "Okay."
    Marina "Да."

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:181
translate spanish hwb_s17_21d26fa4:

    # Amber "Now make most of it red."
    Amber "Теперь бОльшую часть из этого мысленно раскрась в красный."

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:189
translate spanish hwb_s17_d7692e55:

    # "My explanation is met with a vacant stare."
    "Mi explicación se encuentra con una mirada vacía."

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:193
translate spanish hwb_s17_f8bf2925:

    # Amber "I swear, it’s a lot cooler than I’m making it out to be. It’s just kind of hard to explain without pictures."
    Amber "Клянусь, там гораздо круче, чем может показаться из моих объяснений. Просто это трудно описать с помощью слов."

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:197
translate spanish hwb_s17_963a4bcd:

    # Marina "Don’t worry, I believe! Sounds awesome!"
    Marina "Не волнуйся, я верю! Звучит круто!"

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:201
translate spanish hwb_s17_821ce101:

    # Marina "Where is it anyway?"
    Marina "В любом случае, где это?"

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:205
translate spanish hwb_s17_bd3cbbcb:

    # Amber "A little ways into Nevada."
    Amber "По пути в Неваду."

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:209
translate spanish hwb_s17_e3e1c923:

    # Marina "Nevada!"
    Marina "Невада!"

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:211
translate spanish hwb_s17_5c199f12:

    # "Her knees bounce, jolting the table."
    "Sus rodillas rebotan, sacudiendo la mesa."

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:215
translate spanish hwb_s17_4a8e5e7f:

    # Marina "Are we even old enough to gamble?"
    Marina "Мы достаточно взрослые, чтобы играть в азартные игры?"

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:219
translate spanish hwb_s17_08f73576:

    # Amber "There’s more in Nevada than Vegas, dummy."
    Amber "В Неваде есть и другие интересные места, помимо Лас-Вегаса, глупышка."

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:223
translate spanish hwb_s17_2a57dcb8:

    # Marina "Still, isn’t that pretty far?"
    Marina "И все же, разве это не слишком далеко?"

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:227
translate spanish hwb_s17_a32e2459:

    # Amber "That might work to our benefit."
    Amber "Это может  сыграть нам на руку."

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:229
translate spanish hwb_s17_76b14920:

    # Amber "I’ll need to check the map again, but I think we’ll be passing by a place I wanna check out."
    Amber "Мне нужно свериться с картой, но я думаю, что мы будем проезжать место, которое мне хотелось бы посетить."

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:231
translate spanish hwb_s17_fa0446e7:

    # "Her voice brightens."
    "Su voz se ilumina."

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:235
translate spanish hwb_s17_4e16b9f2:

    # Marina "You actually want to go sightseeing?"
    Marina "Ты и правда хочешь посмотреть достопримечательности?"

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:237
translate spanish hwb_s17_e2c6b95c:

    # Amber "Don’t act so surprised. It’s not like I was gonna make a straight shot for California before I picked you up."
    Amber "Чему ты удивляешься. Я не собиралась сразу отправляться в Калифорнию до того, как тебя подобрала."

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:241
translate spanish hwb_s17_5be9e60a:

    # Amber "Besides, I think you might like it."
    Amber "К тому же, я думаю, тебе понравится."

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:243
translate spanish hwb_s17_0da3329c:

    # "Though she does like virtually everything."
    "Aunque le gusta prácticamente todo."

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:247
translate spanish hwb_s17_a5852a06:

    # Amber "It’s a place called Zion."
    Amber "Это место называется Зайон."

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:249
translate spanish hwb_s17_3de6bcbf:

    # Amber "It’s a National Park here in Utah. I hear it's a hell of a lot greener than the places we’ve been through."
    Amber "Это Национальный парк в Юте. Я слышала, что в нем чертовски много зелени, куда больше, чем во всех местах, в которых мы успели побывать."

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:251
translate spanish hwb_s17_0e389504:

    # Amber "I know we’re in a rush, so we won’t stay very long."
    Amber "Я знаю, что мы спешим, так что надолго задерживаться там не будем."

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:255
translate spanish hwb_s17_3864a6ed:

    # "She’s going to burst from excitement, and I still can’t resist messing with her. It’s cute."
    "Va a estallar de emoción, y todavía no puedo resistirme a molestarla. Es lindo."

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:259
translate spanish hwb_s17_e9fc01dc:

    # Amber "But I guess if you don't think we can afford the time..."
    Amber "Но раз уж ты думаешь, что у нас не хватит времени..."

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:261
translate spanish hwb_s17_b60b20c0:

    # "I expect her to throw herself at me. Hug me. Squeeze me with all the energy and happiness she usually does it with."
    "Espero que se lance hacia mí. Que me abrace. Que me apriete con toda la energía y felicidad con la que suele hacerlo."

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:263
translate spanish hwb_s17_23cd76ad:

    # "But she doesn’t."
    "Pero no lo hace."

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:269
translate spanish hwb_s17_3bab9592:

    # "Sitting perfectly still, Marina takes a single breath and gazes at me with a smile."
    "Sentada completamente quieta, Marina toma una sola respiración y me mira con una sonrisa."

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:271
translate spanish hwb_s17_f4afe8cb:

    # Marina "I’ve been surrounded by desert all my life. Seeing green for once would be nice."
    Marina "Меня окружала пустыня всю мою жизнь. Увидеть хоть разок место, богатое растительностью,  было бы прекрасно."

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:273
translate spanish hwb_s17_3ed3e2f4:

    # Marina "I’d love to go with you, Amber."
    Marina "Я была бы рада съездить с тобой, Эмбер."

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:277
translate spanish hwb_s17_cb04f627:

    # "An unsettling hollowness expands in my chest, as I realize I don’t know how to deal with a serious Marina."
    "Un vacío inquietante se expande en mi pecho, al darme cuenta de que no sé cómo lidiar con una Marina seria."

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:279
translate spanish hwb_s17_eadcb67b:

    # Amber "Oh. Alright then."
    Amber "О. Ну тогда хорошо."

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:281
translate spanish hwb_s17_6204181f:

    # "She doesn’t answer. Eyes now closed, arms folded in her lap, the empty, cooperative smile more forced than ever."
    "No responde. Con los ojos cerrados, los brazos cruzados sobre su regazo, la sonrisa vacía y complaciente es más forzada que nunca."

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:285
translate spanish hwb_s17_15bc7cc2:

    # Amber "Well, there’s still a lotta hours left in the day. I’m not sure if we’ll make it in time to check into the campground, but we’ll be close enough that we can do it in the morning if we leave now."
    Amber "Что ж, до конца дня еще полно времени. Не уверена, что его хватит, чтобы успеть заехать в палаточный лагерь, но мы достаточно близко, так что к утру успеем, если поедем сейчас."

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:287
translate spanish hwb_s17_8cca6a15:

    # "Marina nods."
    "Marina asiente."

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:329
translate spanish hwb_s17_a10a20e1:

    # "We scooch out of the booth and walk the ten awkward steps to our seats. Strapping ourselves in, I switch on the ignition, the RV snorting into being."
    "Nos deslizamos fuera del reservado y caminamos los diez pasos incómodos hasta nuestros asientos. Abrochándonos los cinturones, enciendo el motor, y la casa rodante resopla al arrancar."

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:335
translate spanish hwb_s17_c5a5db6a:

    # "I reach for the cassette player, then look to Marina, already lost in her thoughts as she stares out the window."
    "Alcanzo el reproductor de casetes, luego miro a Marina, ya perdida en sus pensamientos mientras mira por la ventana."

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:337
translate spanish hwb_s17_829bdb73:

    # "I don’t have the heart—"
    "No tengo el corazón—"

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:339
translate spanish hwb_s17_bcf6dd4d:

    # "No."
    "No."

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:341
translate spanish hwb_s17_0f4219bb:

    # "I don’t have the courage to snap her out of it this time."
    "No tengo el valor para sacarla de ese estado esta vez."

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:345
translate spanish hwb_s17_8103ba72:

    # "Sighing, I bring my hand back without pressing play and pull the motorhome into drive."
    "Suspirando, retiro mi mano sin presionar play y pongo la casa rodante en marcha."

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:347
translate spanish hwb_s17_96ad2961:

    # "It’s too bad, too."
    "Es una lástima, también."

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:349
translate spanish hwb_s17_1b855d63:

    # "I think I’m really starting to like Marina’s hugs."
    "Creo que realmente estoy empezando a gustarme los abrazos de Marina."

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:371
translate spanish hwb_s17_5eb8ed09:

    # "Hours, and several cups of coffee later, we’ve arrived at our destination. Or, at least close enough to easily check-in in the morning, yet hidden enough to not get towed."
    "Horas, y varias tazas de café después, hemos llegado a nuestro destino. O, al menos lo suficientemente cerca para registrarnos fácilmente por la mañana, pero lo suficientemente escondidos para que no nos remolquen."

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:375
translate spanish hwb_s17_14a4f0f0:

    # "Marina looks to the window, but her eyes drift back over to me, then mine to hers. For one, drawn-out second, our eyes are interlocked, petrified by the other’s stare."
    "Marina mira hacia la ventana, pero sus ojos se desvían hacia mí, luego los míos hacia los suyos. Por un segundo prolongado, nuestros ojos se entrelazan, petrificados por la mirada del otro."

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:381
translate spanish hwb_s17_a274b864:

    # "Then, time continues."
    "Entonces, el tiempo continúa."

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:387
translate spanish hwb_s17_234f4b86:

    # "Our heads swing in the other direction, so fast it takes my mind a few moments to catch up."
    "Nuestras cabezas giran en la dirección opuesta, tan rápido que mi mente tarda unos momentos en ponerse al día."

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:389
translate spanish hwb_s17_6a268649:

    # "The side of her cheek I can still see is flushed."
    "La mejilla que aún puedo ver está sonrojada."

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:391
translate spanish hwb_s17_882613a3:

    # "Glancing in the rear view mirror, I find mine are, too."
    "Mirando en el espejo retrovisor, descubro que las mías también lo están."

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:393
translate spanish hwb_s17_ee294288:

    # "I grip the steering wheel. Then cautiously, without turning my head, look back to Marina. She notices. Our eyes connect again."
    "Aprieto el volante. Luego, con cautela, sin girar la cabeza, miro hacia atrás a Marina. Ella lo nota. Nuestras miradas se cruzan de nuevo."

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:395
translate spanish hwb_s17_a16dd137:

    # "Blush. Rinse. Repeat."
    "Sonrojo. Enjuagar. Repetir."

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:397
translate spanish hwb_s17_4f54ab02:

    # "The past four hours have been excruciating, especially while fighting the urge to throw on music."
    "Las últimas cuatro horas han sido insoportables, especialmente mientras luchaba contra las ganas de poner música."

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:399
translate spanish hwb_s17_f606232d:

    # "I wanted to give Marina the space she needed to say what she has to."
    "Quería darle a Marina el espacio que necesitaba para decir lo que tenía que decir."

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:401
translate spanish hwb_s17_16b44931:

    # "Or give {i}myself{/i} the space to blurt out what {i}I{/i} need to say."
    "O darme {i}a mí misma{/i} el espacio para soltar lo que {i}yo{/i} necesito decir."

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:403
translate spanish hwb_s17_5e7d7041:

    # "It was just…"
    "Solo era que…"

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:407
translate spanish hwb_s17_9596e21b:

    # "Again, Marina looks. I jump. We blush."
    "Otra vez, Marina mira. Yo doy un salto. Nos sonrojamos."

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:411
translate spanish hwb_s17_56b40516:

    # "Never the right time."
    "Nunca era el momento adecuado."

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:451
translate spanish hwb_s17_abc11605:

    # "Deciding I’ve had enough, I hop out of my seat and stretch. Marina follows."
    "Decidiendo que ya tuve suficiente, salto de mi asiento y me estiro. Marina me sigue."

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:453
translate spanish hwb_s17_7b4fa420:

    # "I grab my mug from the holder and drag myself across the scratchy carpet to the sink. A small jolt shocks my finger as I reach for the faucet. The mug slips from my hand and crashes onto the counter, splashing coffee everywhere."
    "Agarro mi taza del portavasos y me arrastro por la alfombra rasposa hasta el fregadero. Una pequeña descarga eléctrica me sorprende el dedo cuando alcanzo el grifo. La taza se me resbala de la mano y se estrella contra la encimera, salpicando café por todas partes."

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:457
translate spanish hwb_s17_1bc8d602:

    # Amber "Crap."
    Amber "Вот черт."

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:461
translate spanish hwb_s17_05702b2f:

    # Marina "Let me help!"
    Marina "Давай помогу!"

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:463
translate spanish hwb_s17_91120cf0:

    # "Marina springs over and reaches for a kitchen rag, but I swat down her hand and grab it just as she does."
    "Marina salta y alcanza un trapo de cocina, pero yo bajo su mano de un manotazo y lo agarro justo cuando ella lo hace."

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:467
translate spanish hwb_s17_bce5b793:

    # Amber "Don’t worry."
    Amber "Не волнуйся."

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:469
translate spanish hwb_s17_df1ed527:

    # "Now we’re forced to look directly at each other, but there’s no blushing this time."
    "Ahora nos vemos obligadas a mirarnos directamente, pero esta vez no hay sonrojos."

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:473
translate spanish hwb_s17_830aac4e:

    # "I nod and pull away the rag as her fingers slide down the fabric."
    "Asiento y retiro el trapo mientras sus dedos se deslizan por la tela."

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:475
translate spanish hwb_s17_5d7de342:

    # Amber "I got this."
    Amber "Я все сделаю."

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:477
translate spanish hwb_s17_78b9fd93:

    # "She stares down at the counter, the spilled coffee trickling onto the floor with a steady drip."
    "Ella mira fijamente la encimera, el café derramado goteando al suelo con un ritmo constante."

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:481
translate spanish hwb_s17_8f7a1145_1:

    # Marina "Oh."
    Marina "Ох."

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:483
translate spanish hwb_s17_9034f3f8:

    # "Without another word, she slouches back to the couch."
    "Sin decir una palabra más, se deja caer en el sofá."

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:487
translate spanish hwb_s17_67821bac:

    # Amber "If you give me a sec, I can setup the bed—"
    Amber "Если дашь мне пару секунд, я разложу кровать—"

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:493
translate spanish hwb_s17_eb8294d3:

    # "The bed’s metal frame slams down with a loud clank that vibrates underneath my feet, followed by the couch cushions swishing past me, landing on the other side of the motorhome." with vpunch
    "Металлический каркас кровати громко падает, заставляя даже пол под ногами вибрировать, а следом мимо меня пролетают подушки до самого дальнего угла трейлера." with vpunch

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:499
translate spanish hwb_s17_e43822c0:

    # Amber "...for ya."
    Amber "...для тебя."

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:501
translate spanish hwb_s17_758a8556:

    # "Dammit."
    "Maldición."

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:505
translate spanish hwb_s17_415c9016:

    # "Whatever. I’ll deal with this in the morning."
    "Como sea. Me ocuparé de esto por la mañana."

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:509
translate spanish hwb_s17_06411229:

    # "I toss the rag into the sink and head to my room, hesitating in front of the slider."
    "Tiro el trapo al fregadero y me dirijo a mi habitación, dudando frente a la puerta corrediza."

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:513
translate spanish hwb_s17_7c165a3f:

    # "Please don’t let it end like this."
    "Por favor, que no termine así."

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:517
translate spanish hwb_s17_037408c8:

    # Marina "Amber!"
    Marina "Эмбер!"

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:519
translate spanish hwb_s17_34a90fd0:

    # "There’s a pause. Several times I hear small gasps, like she’s about to speak, but they all just melt into sighs."
    "Hay una pausa. Varias veces escucho pequeños jadeos, como si estuviera a punto de hablar, pero todos se disuelven en suspiros."

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:527
translate spanish hwb_s17_19f81664:

    # Marina "Goodnight."
    Marina "Спокойной ночи."

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:531
translate spanish hwb_s17_d45c80c6:

    # Amber "‘Night."
    Amber "Спокойной."

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:541
translate spanish hwb_s17_1770b20d:

    # "My hand balls into a fist, my fingernails clawing deep into my skin. I step into the room and shut the slider behind me, immediately throwing my face onto the pillow."
    "Mi mano se cierra en un puño, mis uñas clavándose profundamente en mi piel. Entro a la habitación y cierro la puerta corrediza detrás de mí, enterrando inmediatamente mi cara en la almohada."

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:543
translate spanish hwb_s17_28c9dc81:

    # "I can feel my heart pounding as I roll onto my back. Lying there, twisted up in my sheet, it just keeps beating and beating, never settling down."
    "Puedo sentir mi corazón latiendo mientras me giro boca arriba. Acostada allí, enredada en mi sábana, sigue latiendo y latiendo, sin calmarse nunca."

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:545
translate spanish hwb_s17_63039d91:

    # "Managing to lift myself up on my elbows, I look at the picture next to the slider."
    "Logrando levantarme sobre los codos, miro la foto junto a la puerta corrediza."

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:566
translate spanish hwb_s17_5c8f2dee:

    # "The one with the vinyl sleeve."
    "La que tiene la funda de vinilo."

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:568
translate spanish hwb_s17_67c25df9:

    # "I still remember how his hand felt against my head, from the bony joints of his fingers, to how their calluses massaged my scalp."
    "Todavía recuerdo cómo se sentía su mano contra mi cabeza, desde las articulaciones huesudas de sus dedos, hasta cómo sus callos masajeaban mi cuero cabelludo."

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:570
translate spanish hwb_s17_26f77d1b:

    # "For such a breezy old man, it’s amazing to think just how strong and confident his love was."
    "Para ser un anciano tan despreocupado, es increíble pensar lo fuerte y segura que era su amor."

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:572
translate spanish hwb_s17_bd108f63:

    # "I let my head fall back against the bed and rest my forearm over my face."
    "Dejo caer la cabeza contra la cama y apoyo el antebrazo sobre mi rostro."

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:576
translate spanish hwb_s17_91c019eb:

    # Amber "Ah man, what am I gonna do, Gramps?"
    Amber "Ох, что же мне теперь делать, дедушка?"

# game/script/hwb_s17.rpy:39
translate spanish hwb_s17_db277f66:

    # "Even when the box is closed it radiates a heavy aura, one that’s almost intimidating whenever I come near it."
    "Incluso cuando la caja está cerrada, irradia un aura pesada, una que resulta casi intimidante cada vez que me acerco a ella."

